{"tid":242721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴新一代巴士抵港　將泊屯門車廠","createTime":"2017-05-14T06:40:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T07:09:58.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3d873215e1e7f13001dd2dbf0a86210d60151a83","tid":242721,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T06:40:28.000Z","msg":"九巴在馬來西亞裝嵌的新一代紅色車身巴士，今晚（13日）約8時半在葵涌碼頭抵港，辦妥手續後會駛入屯門車廠停泊，在完成必要的牌照程序後，將盡快投入服務。九巴上周四（4日）在facebook直播新一代巴士在馬來西亞裝嵌的過程，當時預計巴士將於7月投入服務，但未透露將行駛的地區或路線。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新一代巴士車身以紅色為主，有別於現時九巴的金色車身。新巴士車身並印上銀色KMB的字樣及線條，車頂有大片白色圖案，寫上九巴的「城市脈搏」主題。車廂內整體座位位置與現有巴士差不多，座位改為淡啡色，並有新設計以更符合亞洲人身型，車廂前面位置的輪椅位旁，則設有USB充電裝置。<br />\n<br />\n- See more at: <a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170513/s00001/1494685847420#sthash.eHhcwPlN.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170513%2Fs00001%2F1494685847420%23sthash.eHhcwPlN.dpuf&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3cPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=10f7ccd3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170513%2Fs00001%2F1494685847420%23sthash.eHhcwPlN.dpuf&h=1ba827cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170513/s00001/1494685847420#sthash.eHhcwPlN.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"1881a4b644c3ef6646ad7851d13c5df3d62eab87","tid":242721,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T06:48:51.000Z","msg":"新設計以更符合亞洲人身型<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n頂你唔會又窄左丫麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"581e09ca3781874c848f9e62f443a8eeb528ce0b","tid":242721,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T06:51:14.000Z","msg":"新巴士無架好坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17db257cbb7124b5dda15e7049ae247643cd0704","tid":242721,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T06:55:09.000Z","msg":"等睇行B1"},{"pid":"1d06ba902b380072eb7925048a534e9f5104bfcb","tid":242721,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T07:09:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等睇行B1</blockquote><br />\n冇行李架，不了"}]}